{"tid":1022770,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 狂徒插針　81號巴士被插萬字夾　女乘客中招","createTime":"2019-02-15T09:00:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T14:36:53.000Z","uid":54373,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"70d5944647d31e8f96cfb7317682810b71f74c25","tid":1022770,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T09:00:24.000Z","msg":"新巴巴士座椅被插針，一名乘客被刺傷。今（15日）上午約十時，一名女乘客乘搭新巴81號巴士時，疑被尾排左邊第二個座椅上的插針刺傷，遂通知車長和要求下車。車長隨即通知車務控制中心及報警求助，並將巴士停在英皇道1035號惠安苑對開，警察在車上檢獲一根兩厘米長的懷疑萬字夾碎片。該名乘客拒絕送院，自行離開。警員經初步調查，案件列求警調查，由東區警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕。"},{"pid":"40663b1242b11f6f49457ef53d0d31ba91585776","tid":1022770,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T09:01:41.000Z","msg":"唔係觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5361265d8b5ae79012d929731c0f46799f1d080f","tid":1022770,"uid":5649,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T09:03:08.000Z","msg":"N賓又"},{"pid":"3d00dfebed0534d6713ef61064cf55bb5e79ef75","tid":1022770,"uid":1790,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"5361265d8b5ae79012d929731c0f46799f1d080f","tid":1022770,"uid":5649,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T09:03:08.000Z","msg":"N賓又"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T09:08:10.000Z","msg":"咪屈佢放觀塘"},{"pid":"712102e1d6f449f4b0af0f815830839cf516784b","tid":1022770,"uid":99700,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T09:10:43.000Z","msg":"Nben又放自已碌鳩"},{"pid":"9f34fecd110d8a9bbcdd2f5dce0298a2fecc531b","tid":1022770,"uid":58811,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T09:32:05.000Z","msg":"無情的針針針 針入我身"},{"pid":"fc9173fc133dbda1d0a749c562bd7b9f2db29678","tid":1022770,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d00dfebed0534d6713ef61064cf55bb5e79ef75","tid":1022770,"uid":1790,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"5361265d8b5ae79012d929731c0f46799f1d080f","tid":1022770,"uid":5649,"like":12,"di